N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 400.14 - Request for patient review instrument (PRI) data

State Regulations
(a) For purposes of this section, PRI
data
shall mean that data submitted by a residential health care
facility on the PRI forms submitted pursuant to section
86-2.30
of this Part. (b) All requests for PRI data shall be
processed pursuant to section
400.18
of this Part. Notes
